[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 0.21"]]

[[!tag security/current]]

Several security holes affect Tails 0.21.

We **strongly** encourage you to consider [[upgrading to Tails
0.22~rc1|news/test_0.22-rc1]] as soon as possible in case you are
still using an older version. See the [[know issues of Tails
0.22~rc1|news/test_0.22-rc1#known_issues]] before making your
mind, though.

